name: BABYCRYPTOLLAMAS #0171:	Fruity Hot Pink Baby by Psychdre
description: BabyCryptoLlamas are a collection of 3D Animated looped GIFs.  Only 10,000 BabyCryptoLlamas will ever be created. Each one fluffy and unique.  Each BabyCryptoLlama is animated and rendered one at a time. There is no computer algorithm generation. A single 3D animator, Peruvian-American artist Psychdre, creates the llamas.  NFT utility includes holder access to The Llama Lounge Shop online store (launch at 10% sold) . Featured store items include handmade artisan goods (llama toys, alpaca scarfs, Wayuu bags) from South America. Future NFT utility includes Metaverse voxelized cryptollamas.  Collect all the CryptoLlamas and BabyCryptoLlamas!
